{"tid":755354,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"盧偉聰鼓勵年輕人多讀歷史書認識中史","createTime":"2018-07-25T06:53:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-26T06:31:38.000Z","uid":137335,"like":62,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"2e7a3a3e7706039d5efe432d5d6a960d10601696","tid":755354,"uid":137335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T06:53:54.000Z","msg":"警務處處長盧偉聰出席一個書展活動，和青少年交流閱讀心得。<br />\n<br />\n盧偉聰向年輕人推薦了三本書，其中一本是現任外交部副部長傅瑩寫的《我為中國發聲》。他表示，在書中學習到演講的技巧，認為有坦誠和開放的溝通，方能解決問題。<br />\n<br />\n盧偉聰說，現時會閱讀有關工作的書籍，讀書的時候會看歷史書和武俠小說。他又指，書本對他的工作有很大幫助。<br />\n<br />\n盧偉聰鼓勵年輕人多閱讀歷史書，例如<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">三國演義</span></span></strong>，認識中國歷史。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔怪得而家啲官嘅史觀同我地普羅大眾唔同<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 平時睇中國夢打飛機打上腦，連三國演義都變史書<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bcb82b10e49fddc8715c4a6ea986c9da5ad6aa3","tid":755354,"uid":113675,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T06:55:59.000Z","msg":"問下佢識唔識 錢穆 同 傅樂成<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c19ab6f8fbd8caa00dd574c91d95754ace8397e","tid":755354,"uid":13257,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T06:57:01.000Z","msg":"不如讀下中共近代史啦"},{"pid":"089bf6b8b76591dad40990fb1aebab782a4bdfaf","tid":755354,"uid":137335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T06:58:38.000Z","msg":"補返條link<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1408387-20180723.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1408387-20180723.htm&d=FWxduykNtOOU8L%2FspW3vaP%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=4eb2a12e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1408387-20180723.htm&h=04757